<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The construct method of Zend_Validate_PostCode is missing a default value for the $options parameter, seeing as it checks if (null === $options) I would suggest adding '= null' to the constructor so that nothing needs to be passed over if you intend to fetch the locale from the registry.</p>

<ul><li><p>public function __construct($options)</p></li>
<li><ul><li>public function __construct($options = null)</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
